Package com.radiotelescope.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthAdminController
    Rest Controller used to determine if a user is logged in and is an admin
    AuthUserController
    Rest Controller that will grab and return pertinent user authentication information so that it can be stored on login
    BaseRestController
    Abstract class that all REST controllers will extend that takes a class Logger as a parameter so we can handle logging successes and errors. It also has a class Result object that is used to return information to the client
    ExceptionLogger
    System-wide component that will handle any exception experienced strictly within the radio telescope application (see 'basePackages') so the front-end can properly handle whenever an exception occurs. This will also log the exception so that admins can see that it occurred.
